name: Boelo
Lore: 'Naroon Cuthus'' predecessor as Jabba''s right hand man. Sees what he wants to see. Hears what he wants to hear. Has a pet womp rat named Worra.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine or to same site as Jabba. When in a battle either at Audience Chamber or with your alien leader, may cancel one opponent''s battle destiny just drawn.',
